    <Ritual>
        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>Y27.13 Var. a (mss. 40, 88, 400, 410 (sec.m.), 2106):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                … <em>səraošəm xṣ̌aϑrəmcā</em>. taštag kē-š zōhr andar pad sar ī barsom datuš dārišn pad urwēs bē nihišn</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "At ... <em>səraošəm xṣ̌aϑrəmcā</em>, he has to hold the cup that contains the <em>zōhr</em> on the <em>datuš</em> of the <em>barsom</em> and to put it on the <em>urwēs</em>."</ab>
            <ab>Y27.13 Var. b (mss. 15,82): </ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                … <em>səraoṣ̌əm xṣ̌aϑrəmcā</em>. bē afšārišn pad dudīgar pad sidīgar bē afšārišn pad fradom zōhr andar hōm ud harw hōm ud urwarām pālā kardan</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "At ... <em>səraošəm xṣ̌aϑrəmcā</em>, he has to strain (the <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em>). At the second (stanza) and at the third, he has to strain (them). 
                During the first (stanza), he has to pour <em>zōhr</em> into the <em>hōm</em> and to filter each (piece) of <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em>."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
